Token.Abstract: The CatalyzeFileManager class provides an abstracted layer of functionality in order to not clutter to core of the catalyze.io iOS SDK. Network calls were viewed as a separate entity of the SDK entirely. In order to emphasize this, ALL network traffic uploading or downloading files in or out of the SDK goes through this class. The library used for network traffic is AFNetworking found here http://afnetworking.com/ .
